nammoora hammeera ( kannada : ನಮ ಮೂರ ಹಮ ಮೀರ ) is a 1990 indian kannada romantic drama film directed by peraala and written by vijaya bapineedu .   it is a remake of the hugely successful telugu film khaidi no. 786 ( 1988 ) starring chiranjeevi and bhanupriya .   the film features ambareesh , suman ranganathan , devaraj and mukhyamantri chandru in the lead roles .   the film , produced by b. h. bucchi reddy , was widely appreciated for its songs tuned by hamsalekha and lead actors performances upon release .